snippet.textDisplay: Corona.. I've often wonder if I've had this illness already. But the mild form. My mother works in the hospital. And around mid feb I was over to visit. She was sick and my father an brother where as well. From what they told me. They've been sick for roughly 2 weeks.. Within 24 hours of the visit. I took sick. Started off with a tickle in my throat, within a few hours. I was running a fever and chills, body aches. Thats when the stuffed up nose happened. This all lasted for about a week for me. It was the weirdest virus I've experienced. Could've been the flu yes. But what if Corona has been running around before it hit the news. We live in an area where we do bring in Chinese students for flight training. So all it would've took was one to have it when they came over. Went to the hospital, which is where my mother works. Guess we will never know eh. Stay safe everyone !
